snippet.title: The Court Reveals They Don’t Want To Listen To Amber Heard’s Lies Anymore
snippet.description:
►The Court Reveals They Don’t Want To Listen To Amber Heard’s Lies Anymore
The High Court decision came after a three-week circus-like trial in July, during which both Depp and Heard testified and were both harmed by lurid allegations of drinking, drug usage, fighting, and room-trashing. The judge found that "the vast bulk" of Heard's allegations of abuse were mainly true, as given by the tabloid's publisher in its defence.
